=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-aria-valuetext\" aria-label=\"2 aria valuetext permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. aria-valuetext</h2>\n<p>이를 보완하여 다양한 문자열을 사용할 수 있게한 것이라고 보면 된다</p>\n<p>즉 위의 예시에서 ‘40%‘를 정확하게 안내할 수 있으므로 좀 더 사용자 친화적이라 할 수 있다</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuenow</code>와 <code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuetext</code>가 같이 있다면 스크린 리더는 <code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuetext</code>를 우선시한다</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><em>When both the <code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuetext</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuenow</code> are included, the <code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuetext</code> is announced. When there is no <code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuetext</code> attribute, assistive technologies will announce the <code class=\"language-text\">aria-valuenow</code> attribute for the current value.</em></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"references\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#references\" aria-label=\"references permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 